creator: Currensea Limited
descriptionHtml:
Easy - Your bank account, different card
Spend from your bank account when travelling abroad, just with a different card. Life’s too busy to juggle currencies with prepaid cards or different accounts. Just get your Currensea card and go.

Smart - Save 85% on bank charges anywhere in the world

Sustainable - Cut carbon as you spend
Use some (or all) of the savings from your travels to plant trees. We’ll do that for you. $100 spent with Currensea could plant 3 trees! Keep track of your forest with your personalised dashboard.


Five reasons to get your card

1. You stay with your bank
Currensea connects to your main bank account. That means no more prepaid cards or opening up new bank accounts for your travels. No more top-ups, no more managing separate balances, no more hassle.

2. Your money is secure
Your money stays safely in your bank account. Currensea is regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority and registered to use Open Banking technology to connect with your bank.

3. You are in control
Currensea connects to your account just like your bank's debit card. The payments are taken via Direct Debit, and only when you authorise a transaction. Currensea cannot access or store your online banking credentials. You can freeze your card at any time. You're completely in control.

4. You save 85%
Our rates are based on wholesale prices. We don't charge extras such as non-sterling or ATM withdrawal fees, and we don't add extra charges at weekends. Currensea saves 85% on charges vs your bank.

5. You can offset carbon from your travels
• Do it yourself: you can select a % of savings on your bank charges to automatically donate to planting trees in your dashboard. Think of it as an automatic tip.
• We’ll do it for you: you can refer friends, and we’ll plant 6 trees for each referral - 3 for you and 3 for your friend.
descriptionShort: The new way to spend abroad.
